            the festival. Whether as a bidder, organizer, or spectator, everyone contributed to an unforgettable
            experience that showcased the collective spirit of the campus.
          </p>
          <a href="https://drive.google.com/drive/u/0/folders/1XCMAs4m_AKQhOSfbHTAQ1ANauA7Z0F3A" target="_blank"
            class="block w-full text-center bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700 text-white text-xl font-bold tracking-wide px-6 py-5 rounded-xl shadow-xl transition duration-300 ease-in-out">
            View Photos
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="border border-zinc-700 rounded-xl overflow-hidden">
        <button
          class="w-full text-left px-6 py-4 bg-zinc-800 hover:bg-zinc-700 text-purple-400 font-bold text-2xl focus:outline-none toggle-btn">
          Match 1 - Stardust Smashaders VS Feni Flickers
        </button>
        <div class="px-6 py-6 space-y-6 toggle-content hidden">

          <p class="text-yellow-100 text-lg leading-relaxed">
            <span class="block text-xl font-semibold text-purple-300 mb-2">The season opener did not disappoint.</span>
            The first clash of the campaign saw the <span class="font-semibold text-blue-400">Feni Flickers</span> edge
            out the <span class="font-semibold text-blue-400">Stardust Smashaders</span> in a nail‑biting finish. With
            the format demanding the first team to reach four points, the contest went all the way to the final set
            before Feni sealed the win.
          </p>

          <p class="text-yellow-100 text-lg leading-relaxed">
            The Smashaders showed their strength early, taking <span class="font-semibold text-yellow-300">Singles
              C</span> and <span class="font-semibold text-yellow-300">Doubles</span> convincingly. But the Flickers
            refused to back down. Captain <span class="font-semibold">Veer</span> produced a clutch
            performance, saving two match points against Stardust captain <span class="font-semibold ">Abhinav</span> to
            keep his side alive and deny what could have been a
            massive upset in the very first match of the season.
          </p>

          <p class="text-yellow-100 text-lg leading-relaxed">
            The decider came down to <span class="font-semibold">Aarush</span>, who faced <span
              class="font-semibold ">Ammar</span> in a tense battle that pushed the game to <span
              class="font-semibold text-yellow-300">12–14</span>. Aarush held his nerve, saving two match points and
            delivering the final blow that secured the Flickers’ dramatic triumph.
          </p>

          <p class="text-yellow-100 text-xl font-bold leading-relaxed border-t border-zinc-600 pt-4">
            Final Score: <span class="text-green-400">Feni Flickers 4</span> – <span class="text-red-400">Stardust
              Smashaders 3</span><br>
            <span class="text-purple-300 font-medium">A thrilling start to the season, setting the tone for the battles
              ahead.</span>
          </p>
          <a href="/tournament/matches/match-1"
            class="block w-full text-center bg-green-600 hover:bg-green-700 text-white text-xl font-bold tracking-wide px-6 py-5 rounded-xl shadow-xl transition duration-300 ease-in-out">
            View the full match HERE
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>

